	@printf "⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⠠⠛⢃⡋⢗⢃⣵⠾⡿⡫⢄⡃$(PURPLE)⠀⠀⠈⠀⠀⠙⠟⢿⣿⣿⣿⡿⢶⣦⠄⠩⠂⠈⢿⡰⠀⠀⠈⢳⡠⠀⢡⣿⡝⡶⠀⡞⡄⣀⠀⠀⠀⠎⢙⣭⡟$(YELLOW)⠀⠀⢿⣷⣶⣾⡿⠄⠉$(RESET)⠸⡄⣾⢺⢄⠵⡄⡇⢟⣅⣿⠸⠁⡇⢿⡌⢏⢿⡀⠉⠻⣿⡄⠑⡀⠁⠙⣄⠻⣆⠀⢻⡄⠂⠄⠀⠄⠻⣌⠏⣦⣼⣧⣈⣿⣾⣥⣢⡤⣄⡀⠀⠀⠀$(RESET)\n"
