	@printf "⠀$(YELLOW)⣠⡾⡿⠂⡰⠀$(RESET)⣤⣧⣄⠒⠀⠀⠥⠀⠀⠒⢒⠀⠀⢤⡄$(RED)⠐⠀⠀⡀$(RESET)⠀⠻⢿⣿⣷⣶⡱⢠⠠⣤⠔⢤⠚⢂⢢⡄⢀⡘⠃⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⢠⣿⣄⠀⠀⠙⠀⠀⠈⠁⠈$(RED)⡏⠇⠈⠔⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼$(RESET)⠝⡠⠃⠈⠆⠈⠀⠡⠀⠌⢦⣀⠙⢠⠀⡀⣶⣄⡐⠸⡀⢻⡀⡜⠌⡳⣓⠽⡿⠛⠡⠒⠙⠿⢿⣿⣓⢁⣠⠺⣿⡆$(RESET)\n"
	@printf "⠀⣩⣵⣃⠀⠁⡴⣿⣟⣯$(RED)⠰⡦⠐⠐⠶⠂⢀⣨⣤⣶⠞⠁⠐⢶⢶⠇⡀⠀⠈⢙⠿⢫$(RED)⢃⣾⡦⡉⠀⣈⠦⢊⠺⡷⠺⠁⠀⡐⠂⠀⠀⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⢠⣾⣿⣿⣦⣀⢀⡀$(RESET)⠀⠀⢀⠠⢱⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀$(RED)⡀$(RESET)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢉⣴⠃⢀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠠⣄⠐⢮⠛⢠⣌⠀⢣⡿⣽⣧⠀⢣⠘⣇⢡⠐⢳⣽⡔⠡⢀⣠⣆⠀⠐⠚⢯⢛⣬⡯⠴⣿⡓$(RESET)\n"
	@printf "⠀⢉⣉⠛⠿⡆⣯⣉⡭⠍⢂⡔⠂⠀⠀⠁$(RED)⠻⣿⣿⠁⠀⢀⠘⡠⢜⣀⡾⠀⠀⠀⠀$(RED)⢃⢸⡏⢩⣕⠊⠀⠉⠂⠀⠠⢂⡀⠀⠡⣓⡀⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⢀⣿⣿⣿$(RESET)⣟⢹⣿⠿⣪⣿⣿⣈⠤⠈⠁$(RED)⣤⣶⡿⠉⠩⣥⠀⠀⠀⠀$(RESET)⠉⣠⢆⠀⡣⠍⠱⠷⣒⣬⡺⣬⣿⣥⣶⣶⣶⣿⣿⣿⠀⠈⠀⠨⠈⠑⠒⠙⢏⠀⢹⣿⣿⣶⣒⠩⠑⢽⢩⠉⠀⠘⠃$(RESET)\n"
	@printf "⠀⠈⠛⠿⣦⢀⠐⠆⡠⢀⡒⠀$(RED)⢲⡿⡿⣝⣕⣌⡳⠀$(RED)⠀⢠⠀⢛⡓⣉⡕⠐⡀$(RED)⣴⣦⡌⢸⡱⠋⠈⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⠃⠠⡒⠋⠀⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⣸⣿$(RESET)⣫⣶⡾⣦⡀⢰⡙⣣⠞⣫⠴⡲⠦$(RED)⠢⢹⣶⣧⣠⣿⡃⠀⠀$(RESET)⡀⢼⡚⢇⡂⠉⣷⢿⣿⣿⡿⠁⢹⣿⣿⣿⣿⡿⠛⠉⠁⠀⠀⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⢿⣽⣿⢆⢐⠄⡛⣁⢦⠀⠀\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀⠀⢀⣐⠮⠥⠄⣀⡠$(RED)⡀⢶⡿⡇⠹⠜⠎⢫⡄⠁$(RED)⠀⡄⢩⣐⡉⠌⡈⠴$(RED)⠀⠉⠉⠀⠘⣠⡄⠀⢀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⡇⢀⡠⠄⠀⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⣿⠃$(RESET)⠈⠻⡧⠹⢯⠳⣣⠉⠊⡔⠣⠄⠙⢻$(RED)⣦⠛⠙⢿⡿⠀⠀$(RESET)⠈⠣⢀⠑⠆⠙⠤⠀⠙⣿⣻⡵⣖⠤⢿⣿⣿⣿⡇⠀⠀⠀⠁⠀⠀⢠⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣶⣦⣰⡀⠀⠀⠀⠋⠈⠀⠀\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀⣰⣭⣛⡛⣛⣫⠍$(RED)⠀⠧⠀⠘⠈⣀⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀$(RED)⠐⠃⠈⠻⠏⠀⠀⣱$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⠑⠠⣦⣨⣬⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼⣇⡉⡸⠁⠀⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⢹⠀⡀$(RESET)⠔⢊⠵⠉⠂⠀⠠⢶⣶⠶⣦⣄⠀⠺⢕⣰⠂⠚⡟⢧⣉⠐⡒⢄⠠⠁⣀⠁⠀⠀⠁⠛⢼⣫⣭⣿⣿⢟⣾⡦⠀⠀⢐⠎⢗⠈⢰⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⣿⣿⣷⢵⣕⣔⣀⡀⠀⣠⡇\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⢹⣛⣙⠁⠨⠡⠄⠀⠀⠀⠀⣌⣿⣷⣾⠟⣱⡇$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡰⠁$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠳⠦⠙⠿⠮⠉⠀⠀⠀⣉⠅⠀⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⠘$(RESET)⠄⠘⠀⢃⠒⡡⠄⢤⠩⢍⠈⠓⢡⠈⠓⡀⠀⢹⡀⠈⢀⠃⢚⡓⠦⠈⢂⠦⣐⠦⣄⠤⢀⠀⠀⠀⠋⠉⢠⡾⠃⣠⡧⠀⢼⠎⠈⢿⣆⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⠿⠻⠟⣸⡞⣿⣿⣿⣿⣷⣽\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⢷⡍⠿⣀⠀⣀⡠⠂⣀⠀⠀⠙⠛⠿⢫⠦⠉⣀⠀⠀⠐⡀⡄$(RED)⠀⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠰⣬⡆⡿⠀⠁⠀⠀⠀$(RED)⢠⣋⠡⡌⠥⢉⠄⡐⣂⠒⠢⠄⣈⠥⢘⡂⠁$(RED)⠀⠑⡀⡇⢨⡄⢀⠘⠣⠙⠐⠀⢂⠆⠙⠖⠀⢠⠀⠔⠑⣢⠤⠛⣈⣥⠾⠿⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⢠⠖⢶⣚⠗⣩⢾⠿⠿⢍⣝⣳⣭\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⠈⠉⠈⣼⡶⢛⡑⠄⢀⢖⣦⣦⠲⠈⣠⡆⠂⠹⠛⠽⢿⣿⡿⢍⣴⣆$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡀⠄⠜⠐⢠⠀$(RED)⢀⠔⢛⣫⣷⡟⡰⢂⠌⢀⡑⢦⣙⡰⣦⡐⡙⢶⡈⡀$(RED)⠀⠠⣣⡴⣮⣤⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⡀⠀⢀⣠⣡⣄⠶⠘⢋⣼⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢠⠆⠀⢀⣫⣻⠛⠁⠌⣋⣤⢷⣾⣻⢿⡿⣟\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⠠⣌⡄⣿⣅⠘⠀⠀⣌⣿⣿⣿⠁⢀⠗⣀⢯⢻⡇$(RED)⢀⣿⡎⢙⣆⡉⠿⠆⣠⣀⠀$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣿⠀⠀⢠⠃⠀$(RED)⢀⠴⢋⣽⠿⡼⢳⠃⢀⣤⡸⢢⡝⣿⣮⡻⢮⠲⡙⣄$(RED)⢢⢠⣅⠛⣫⡾⣷⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⠐⡐⠲⡅⡤⠟⠋⣉⢠⡔⢞⣾⡇⠀⣀⠐⠒⣒⣀⠀⠀⠀⡞⡀⠀⠀⠘⠁⣀⠶⠩⠛⠯⣿⡼⣏⡿⣵⢫\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⠐⠀⠀⣿⣿⠀⣰⣦⢸⡏⡆⡿⠀⢰⣏⣏$(RED)⡈⠘⢃⣰⣜⢷⣌⢿⣿$(RED)⡘⣷⣦⡉⠃⠉⠑⡀$(RED)⢀⠒⠀⡀⠀⠀⠈⠂$(RED)⠀⠀⠈⢠⠙⠁⠘⠁⢀⠀⢾⣿⣧⠁⠻⠑⡉⢓⠀⠀⠂⠴⡈⢖⣤⠦⣄⣘⣩⠴⣾⣶⡆⠀⠀⣀⡤⢠⠈⡃⠕⢞⠛⠋⡀⣴⡿⢊⡀⠰⡭⣤⣜⡛⠯⣷⢦⣄⠸⠈⠀⡀⠀⠀⠙⢾⡀⠀⠈⠀⠈⠉⠓⢭⣥\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⣱⡀⢸⣿⣿⡎⣿⠇⢸⢱⠇⠀⠀⣾⢸⢹⣇$(RED)⠛⢈⢳⣿⣮⢿⣷⣿⣷⢠$(RED)⡛⢿⣶⣄⡀⠀⠀⠀⠁⣠⣤⣶⣶⣾⣷⣶⣄$(RED)⠂⠀⠄⠀⠀⢈⢘⡊⣿⣿⠀⡄⢡⠀⠀⠡⢀⠈⠄⠸$(RED)⣜⣷⣾⣿⣿⣿⣿⡶⢩⠆⣀⣤⣶⣦⣕⠂⡈⠆⢸⣿⡌⠁⢀⢠⡩⠗⡀⠙⠚⠶⢹⠳⠖⠋⠓⢠⣤⣖⢍⣢⢀⠠⡶⢊⣀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠤⠘⠛\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⠘⠀⡘⣿⠸⠃⠁⠀⠘⢬⠈⠀⢐⢯⠬⡜⠃$(RED)⠉⡄⡧⢻⢿⣧⢹⣿⢿⠏⢿⡀$(RED)⠈⠋⠀⠀⠀⣀⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣟⢿⣷⡄$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⡿⠐⠁⢾⡿⣘⠁⣰⡆⢰⠀⠀⠂⢉⢎$(RED)⣾⣿⣿⠿⠿⠟⢋⡁⢳⣿⣿⢙⣏⢿⡿⠀⠀⠀⡾⠉⠀⠰⢊⠁⠀⠀⠘⢤⡀⢀⡀⠐⠃⠀⠻⣱⣌⠛⢷⣮⡠⠉⡠⡽⣿⣿⣿⡿⠿⠿⠓⠒\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠘⠀⠀⠀⠀⠰⠎⠃⠀⠮⢍⣊$(RED)⠀⡆⡀⠁⢉⣀⠸⢻⠅⢿⠘⠀⠘⡇$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢼⣿⢟⡡⣦⣤⠤⠐⣈⢻⡏⠐$(RED)⠀⠀⢸⣿⣷⡚⢘⣿⣯⡴⡖⠂⢀⠀⠀⡀⡦⣿⢟⡵⠚⢉⣤⣷⡿⣣⡐⡠⠹⣾⣿⣦⡀⠀⠀⣌⡵⣶⢫⠁⢇⡂⠀⣠⣄⡄⠒⢉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡀⢀⣀⣂⣐⣾⣦⡃⢷⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⠠⣄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀$(RED)⢠⢆⢇⠉⠄⠚⢷⡀⠈⠄⠈⠀⢠⡄⠀$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢨⣿⣿⣯⣱⠊⣟⣥⣧⣾⢛⢷⣄⠀$(RED)⠀⠹⣿⡷⢾⣿⢿⣿⣷⣤⠾⢀⣀⣐$(RED)⠉⠡⢁⣤⣾⣿⢟⣯⣿⡿⠛⠀⠥⠙⠫⢱⡒⠒⠈⢻⠟⣰⠃⠀⣊⡠⠜⠛⢣⣄⠴⠾⠓⠤⢔⡬⣲⢭⣛⡼⡣⠟⠳⢻⠃⢸⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⠀⠀⠐⡂⠄⣀⢆⣭⣿⣤⣤⠃⠆⠀$(RED)⠠⣾⣿⣆⡄⢀⡶⠁⠀⡀⠀⠀⠆⠉⠐$(RED)⠀⠀⡠⠄⡀⢸⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣏⠼⠢⠻⣧⡁$(RED)⠀⠈⢻⡕⣽⢯⠿⣉⢁⣽⣿⠿⠋$(RED)⣠⣷⣿⣿⢟⣵⠿⢋⠡⢀⢐⣠⡆⠀⠀⠀⠃⠁⠂⢀⠘⠃⠒⠈⢩⠀⣚⡍⢛⣭⢡⢪⢋⡟⠙⠒⠃⠛⠈⠁⢀⡤⠄⠒⠀⢸⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀$(RED)⠀⢠⡾⢋⠾⢡⠀⡿⡟⠺⢶⣅⠐⠄$(RED)⠑⢻⡿⠚⠀⠈⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀$(RED)⠀⠀⢴⡀⠈⠲⣙⠻⢿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⢦⣴⡤⠀$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⣿⠠⠒⢢⡴⢶⠞$(RED)⢄⡖⣿⣿⢟⢱⡟⢁⠒⠌⣀⡾⠛⠿⡦⢄⠀⠀⠩⠦⢤⠉⠠⡀⠀⠀⢸⠄⠡⠠⠏⠹⠂⠀⠈⣀⠤⠠⠤⠀⠀⠀⠀⠃⠀⠀⠀⢸⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n"
	@printf "⠀⠀⠀⠃⠁⠈⠘⠀⠀⠁⠁⠀⠀⠈⠁⠁⠀⠈⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀$(RED)⠀⠀⠈⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠛⠙⠋⠉⠐⠉⠁⠀$(RED)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠂⠘⠀⠐⠈⠉⠃⠀$(RED)⠚⠉⠛⠁⠈⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠓⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠚⠁⠀⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n"
	
$(OBJS_DIR) $(OBJ_SUBDIRS) :
	@mkdir -p $@

-include $(DEPS)

$(OBJS_DIR)/%.o: $(SRCS_DIR)/%.c | $(OBJ_SUBDIRS)
	@printf "$(LBLUE)[Compilation]$(RESET) In progress... $(GREEN)$<" && \
	$(CC) $(CFLAGS) -I$(HEADERS) -c $< -o $@ && \
	printf "\r$(LBLUE)[Compilation]$(RESET) Completed   ... $(GREEN)$<" && \
	printf " $(LBLUE)[$(RESET)$(CC)$(LBLUE)/]$(RESET)\n"

clean:
	@make --silent clean -C ${MLXDIR}
	@make --silent clean -C ${LIBFTDIR}
	@rm -rf $(OBJS_DIR)
	@printf "                                                                                                          \r$(GREEN)$(NAME) is Clean\n$(RESET)"

	
fclean: clean
	@rm -f $(LIBFTDIR)/libft.a
	@rm -f $(NAME)  
	
re: fclean all

.PHONY : all clean fclean re 
	